<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify your email address</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Verify your email address</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up for Planora! To complete your registration, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your email address:</p>
        
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #007bff; letter-spacing: 5px;"><%= otp %></h1>
        </div>
        
        <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Planora Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
